29#ifndef __NOUVEAU_CRTC_H__
30#define __NOUVEAU_CRTC_H__
31
32#include <nvif/notify.h>
33
34struct nouveau_crtc {
35 struct drm_crtc base;
36
37 int index;
38 struct nvif_notify vblank;
39
40 uint32_t dpms_saved_fp_control;
41 uint32_t fp_users;
42 int saturation;
43 int color_vibrance;
44 int vibrant_hue;
45 int sharpness;
46 int last_dpms;
47
48 int cursor_saved_x, cursor_saved_y;
49
50 struct {
51 int cpp;
52 bool blanked;
53 uint32_t offset;
54 uint32_t handle;
55 } fb;
56
57 struct {
58 struct nouveau_bo *nvbo;
59 bool visible;
60 uint32_t offset;
61 void (*set_offset)(struct nouveau_crtc *, uint32_t offset);
62 void (*set_pos)(struct nouveau_crtc *, int x, int y);
63 void (*hide)(struct nouveau_crtc *, bool update);
64 void (*show)(struct nouveau_crtc *, bool update);
65 } cursor;
66
67 struct {
68 struct nouveau_bo *nvbo;
69 uint16_t r[256];
70 uint16_t g[256];
71 uint16_t b[256];
72 int depth;
73 } lut;
74
75 int (*set_dither)(struct nouveau_crtc *crtc, bool update);
76 int (*set_scale)(struct nouveau_crtc *crtc, bool update);
77 int (*set_color_vibrance)(struct nouveau_crtc *crtc, bool update);
78};
79
80static inline struct nouveau_crtc *nouveau_crtc(struct drm_crtc *crtc)
81{
82 return crtc ? container_of(crtc, struct nouveau_crtc, base) : NULL;
83}
84
85static inline struct drm_crtc *to_drm_crtc(struct nouveau_crtc *crtc)
86{
87 return &crtc->base;
88}
89
90int nv04_cursor_init(struct nouveau_crtc *);
91
92#endif /* __NOUVEAU_CRTC_H__ */
93
